{"title":"死神日记——深渊三部曲","date":"2025-06-09T21:20:00.000Z","updated":"2026-04-27T10:00:04.431Z","comments":true,"path":"api/pages/-----------.json","covers":null,"excerpt":null,"content":"<h4 id=\"作者：伴莺-·-Wled\"><a href=\"#作者：伴莺-·-Wled\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"作者：伴莺 · Wled\"></a>作者：<font color=gold>伴莺 · Wled</font></h4><details class=\"relative my-4 border border-border-color bg-second-background-color rounded-md  blue\" data-header-exclude><summary class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-md shadow-[0_0_2px_0_var(--shadow-color-1)] cursor-pointer not-markdown\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i>免责声明</summary><div class=\"content p-4 \"><p><strong><font color=green>Thank you for your visit.</font></strong></p>\n<div class=\"callout callout--simple danger mb-4 rounded-small shadow-redefine-flat bg-(--callout-bg-color) p-3 pl-1 relative flex flex-row gap-2 items-center\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"rounded-full self-stretch w-0.5 bg-(--callout-primary-color) shrink-0 opacity-60\"></div><div class=\"callout__content markdown-body flex-1 min-w-0\"><p>本作品首发<font color=green>伴莺の小窝</font>，未经授权<font color=red>禁止搬运！</font></p></div></div>\n<div class=\"callout callout--simple warning mb-4 rounded-small shadow-redefine-flat bg-(--callout-bg-color) p-3 pl-1 relative flex flex-row gap-2 items-center\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"rounded-full self-stretch w-0.5 bg-(--callout-primary-color) shrink-0 opacity-60\"></div><div class=\"callout__content markdown-body flex-1 min-w-0\"><p>作品中包含部分AI内容，用于校正、完善文章，如有错误请向管理员反馈。</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"callout callout--simple info mb-4 rounded-small shadow-redefine-flat bg-(--callout-bg-color) p-3 pl-1 relative flex flex-row gap-2 items-center\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"rounded-full self-stretch w-0.5 bg-(--callout-primary-color) shrink-0 opacity-60\"></div><div class=\"callout__content markdown-body flex-1 min-w-0\"><p>作品中的人名、地名、世界观、物品名称、角色行为等纯属虚构，如有雷同纯属巧合。</p></div></div></div></details>\n\n<hr>\n<p>在几年<del class=\"mask\">的口水话叙述、几年三部曲的创作和几年设定</del>的缝缝补补之后，这部自立项开始创作了近7年的作品也是可以发布了。</p>\n<p>创作之初，其实并没有很宏大的构想，更多的，只是不成熟的、留有稚气的天真幻想。但立项开始，小说就致力于<font color=purple>虚幻</font>和<font color=gren>现实</font>共存。所以，无论是主角的死亡，还是主角和某人的相遇，都尽可能的贴近真实发生的史料。这也是小说迟迟难以重制的原因之一……</p>\n<p>当然，多说无益，还可能会背刺自己<del class=\"mask\">（绝对不是还有坑我没填完）</del>，这个页面会随着小说的更新一起更新，届时一些设定应该也会完善哦~</p>\n<p>不管怎么样，<strong>我很高兴你能阅读这部小说！</strong></p>\n<p>小说更新时间线和目录见下文。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"小说目录\"><a href=\"#小说目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"小说目录\"></a>小说目录</h3><div class=\"tabs relative my-4 bg-second-background-color border border-border-color rounded-md\" id=\"tab-menu\"><div role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" class=\"flex gap-3.5 overflow-x-auto px-4 not-markdown scrollbar-hide\" tabindex=\"0\"><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" data-state=\"active\" data-tab=\"menu-1\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-third-text-color border-b-2 border-transparent py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-second-text-color data-[state=active]:border-primary data-[state=active]:text-primary\" tabindex=\"0\"><font color=green>【连载】</font> 深渊</button><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-state=\"inactive\" data-tab=\"menu-2\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-third-text-color border-b-2 border-transparent py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-second-text-color data-[state=active]:border-primary data-[state=active]:text-primary\" tabindex=\"-1\"><font color=gray>【待定】</font> 空壳</button><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-state=\"inactive\" data-tab=\"menu-3\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-third-text-color border-b-2 border-transparent py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-second-text-color data-[state=active]:border-primary data-[state=active]:text-primary\" tabindex=\"-1\"><font color=gray>【待定】</font> 余音</button></div><div class=\"tab-content p-4 bg-background-color/70 rounded-md shadow-[0_0_2px_0_var(--shadow-color-1)]\"><div class=\"tab-pane\" data-state=\"active\" id=\"menu-1\"><p><code>随缘更新一章节的若干段（若干篇日记），</code></p>\n<p>序——普度众生：<font color=green>已重置！</font><a class=\"button not-markdown\" href=\"../2026/04/27/DarknessRe0\" title=\"点击阅读\"><i class=\"fa-solid\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> 点击阅读</a><br>第一章：<font color=gray>待定</font> </p></div><div class=\"tab-pane\" data-state=\"inactive\" id=\"menu-2\" hidden><p>未更新，目录不可查看。</p></div><div class=\"tab-pane\" data-state=\"inactive\" id=\"menu-3\" hidden><p>未更新，目录不可查看。</p></div></div></div><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://unpkg.com/markmap-toolbar@0.18.10/dist/style.css\"><script src=\"https://unpkg.com/d3@7\"></script><script src=\"https://unpkg.com/markmap-view@0.18.10\"></script><script src=\"https://unpkg.com/markmap-toolbar@0.18.10\"></script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/markmap.css\">\n\n<script src=\"/js/markmap.js\"></script>\n"}